      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">When to Play AA in Scrabble</h2>

      <p>AA scores only 2 points base, so you never play it just for the score. Its value is entirely strategic.</p>

